Class HashList

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.arjuna.ArjunaCommon.Template.HashList
public class HashList
extends java.lang.Object

This hash table for objects which define get_uid does not use the Java Hashtable class, since we sometimes want to add multiple different values under the same key.

Since:
JTS 1.0.
